PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the YUKON TERRITORY which provides for the implementation of a financial arrangement, through the Canada-Yukon Formula Financing Agreement of May 15, 1991, whereby the Government of Canada will provide financial assistance to the Yukon for the provision of hospital care and medical services for Indians.
